## ✅ Week 1: System Architecture & User Management

🛠 **Tasks:**
1. Create 3 users: `brian`, `tina`, and `sue`, each with:
   - Custom shell: `/bin/bash`
   - Expiry date: 30 days from today
   - Primary group: `staff`   
[sudo adduser brian/tina/sue -S /path/to/shell && sudo groupadd staff && sudo usermod -aG staff brian/tina/sue && sudo passwd -x 30 brian/tina/sue] 
2. Create a group called `developers` and add `tina` and `sue` to it. 
[sudo groupadd developers && sudo usermod -aG developers tina/sue]
3. Lock `brian`'s account. 
[sudo passwd -l brian]
4. Set `tina`’s password to expire in 15 days and force password change on next login. 
[sudo passwd -x 15 && sudo passwd -e]
5. Check user info using `id`, `getent`, `lastlog`.
[id brian && getent brian && lastlog brian]

