[sudo hostnamectl set-hostname "lfcs-node01"]
3. Add `192.168.1.200 testbox.local` to `/etc/hosts`
[echo "192.168.1.200 testbox.local" >> /etc/hosts]
4. Disable SSH root login and change SSH port to `2222` in `/etc/ssh/sshd_config`
[Study-Logs/study-week-4/sshd_config]
